Description




DMG Entertainment and Media Co., Ltd. is a China-based media company. The Company is principally engaged in entertainment film and television content and advertising marketing services businesses. Its major services include brand management, advertising production, brand promotion, brand public relations, entertainment marketing, as well as film and television derivative services, among others. The Company distributes its products in domestic market and to overseas markets.


