Company Overview of DMG Entertainment and Media Co., Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
DMG Entertainment and Media Co., Ltd. operates as an entertainment and media company in China. The company is involved in motion pictures, media, television, music, digital, and other entertainment businesses. It also provides POS, print, radio, and television advertising services; and creative management services, as well as branded content, and PR and event services. The company is based in Beijing, China.


Tower ALevel 2526 Chaoyangmenwai StreetBeijing,  100020China423 Employees



Phone: 86 10 8565 3333

www.dmgmedia.com







