DMG Entertainment and Media Co., Ltd. Key Developments

DMG Announces Dividend Implementation on A Shares for the Year 2016
Jul 12 17
DMG announced dividend implementation with cash dividend (tax included) of CNY 0.90000000 per 10 shares on A shares for the year 2016. Record date is July 18, 2017, ex-date is July 19, 2017 and payment date is July 19, 2017. Net cash dividend after tax was CNY 0.81000000 per 10 shares.


DMG Entertainment and Media Co., Ltd., Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Jul 14, 2017
Jun 29 17
DMG Entertainment and Media Co., Ltd., Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Jul 14, 2017, at 15:00 China Standard Time. Agenda: To consider extension of trading suspension for planning of major assets restructuring.


DMG Entertainment and Media Co., Ltd., Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Jun 08, 2017
May 24 17
DMG Entertainment and Media Co., Ltd., Special/Extraordinary Shareholders Meeting, Jun 08, 2017, at 15:00 China Standard Time. Agenda: To consider issue of short-term financing bills.


