Company Profile
Sector: Communications
Industry: Media
Sub-Industry: Entertainment Content
DMG Entertainment & Media Co. Ltd., specializes in the production and distribution of animation, radio, and TV media. The Company also produces entertainment and cultural information and advertising, in addition to public relations consulting and professional training.




